
Review Schedule

· When: First week of each quarter (Jan, Apr, Jul, Oct)
· Duration: 2-3 days maximum
· Responsible: Engineering Managers + Product Owners

Review Checklist

A. Property Health Check

1. Usage Analysis
   ```sql
   -- Example queries to run:
   SELECT "Priority Level", COUNT(*) as count 
   FROM issues 
   GROUP BY "Priority Level" 
   ORDER BY count DESC;
   
   · Identify unused/underused options
   · Check for option duplication
   · Verify consistency across teams
2. Option Rationality
   · Remove options used < 5 times in last quarter
   · Merge similar options (e.g., "UI" + "Frontend")
   · Add new options if recurring manual entries exist